The `@nx/jest/plugin` is configured in the `plugins` array in `nx.json`.

```json {% fileName="nx.json" %}
{
  "plugins": [
    {
      "plugin": "@nx/jest/plugin",
      "options": {
        "targetName": "test"
      }
    }
  ]
}
```

*   The `targetName` option controls the name of the inferred Jest tasks. The default name is `test`.
